		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>It looks to me like add_filter(&#8216;xmlrpc_enabled&#8217;,&#8217;__return_false&#8217;) does NOT prevent pingbacks in wp 3.8.1, it&#8217;s only checked in wp_xmlrpc_server::login, which isn&#8217;t used for pingbacks. </p>
<p>&#8216;xmlrpc_call&#8217; is checked for pingbacks.</p>
		</div>

		
		
